{"tid":1286132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急！一定要入黎傾好佢！文宣巴絲","createTime":"2019-07-04T19:19:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T19:22:57.000Z","uid":268373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a26044fc2424741b2b1da55f2be1a5384c3ca92f","tid":1286132,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T19:19:46.000Z","msg":"發夢見到段文字，而家打返段文字出黎 <br />\n而家武漢有起義，證明香港人呢個月反抗、抗爭既行為同思想可能已經傳入大陸<br />\n我地要利用我地網路仲係自由既優勢，大大力用文宣力量洗入大陸 <br />\n我建議可以send唔同既圖入大陸網上平台 <br />\n一黎可以表示香港人支持武漢人既抗議<br />\n一黎可以順便宣傳埋唔好再屈服係共產黨之下<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span>記得唔好直接send比中國既朋友、親戚 佢地手機有呢D圖好大鑊<br />\n係D陸媒留言板、小紅書乜都好、貼下圖、留下言咁<br />\n以下歡迎各位留底你認為合適既文宣圖！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a704daf2603c0172c62942c574dc058e9e41f140","tid":1286132,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T19:19:59.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"9016841e703a41e1043913d8d3031e0811bd7d61","tid":1286132,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T19:20:13.000Z","msg":"我有野講呀！入黎啦！"},{"pid":"8f1e5bec43b7208fbc63778327cfe8b02d8a52c8","tid":1286132,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T19:20:33.000Z","msg":"Comecomecome <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"693fe7caf91c5b5dfa45aafd94f3356dfc41c598","tid":1286132,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T19:20:48.000Z","msg":"Yellow C A R D ~"},{"pid":"6be